26:44.077 --> 26:45.860
What does that come to a crate?

26:45.878 --> 26:49.548
A fuck of a lot more than you're paying for it.
That's for sure.

26:49.582 --> 26:51.717
Do we have a deal or no?

26:54.504 --> 26:57.889
- Dirty chiseler. - You'll hear from
